import json
def hive_ddl(HIVE_DB, SCHEMA, HIVE_TABLE_NAME, HDFS_PATH, PARTITION=None, CLUSTERING=None, CLUSTERING_NB=1000): MAPPER = {'string': 'STRING', 'long': 'BIGINT', 'float': 'DOUBLE', 'string': 'STRING', 'boolean': 'BOOLEAN', 'int': 'INT', 'double': 'DOUBLE'} hive_ddl_schema, fields_name, fields_type = [], [], []
for k in SCHEMA['fields']: fields_name.append(k["name"]) if k["type"][1] == 'null': fields_type.append(k["type"][0]) else: fields_type.append(k["type"][1])
if PARTITION in fields_name: hive_partition = "(" + PARTITION + " " + MAPPER[fields_type[fields_name.index(PARTITION)]] + ")" fields_type.pop(fields_name.index(PARTITION)) fields_name.remove(PARTITION) else: hive_partition = None
if CLUSTERING in fields_name: hive_clustering = CLUSTERING else: hive_clustering = None
for k, v in zip(fields_name, fields_type): hive_ddl_schema.append("`" + k + "`" + " " + MAPPER[v])
hive_ddl_schema = '(' + ', '.join(hive_ddl_schema) + ')' ddl = [] ddl.append("CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS " + HIVE_DB + "." + HIVE_TABLE_NAME + " " + hive_ddl_schema) if hive_partition: ddl.append("PARTITIONED BY " + hive_partition) if hive_clustering: ddl.append("CLUSTERED BY (" + hive_clustering + ") INTO " + str(CLUSTERING_NB) + " BUCKETS") ddl.append("STORED AS AVRO " + "\n") ddl.append("LOCATION \'" + HDFS_PATH + "/" + HIVE_TABLE_NAME + "\';") ddl.append("MSCK REPAIR TABLE " + HIVE_DB + "." + HIVE_TABLE_NAME + ";") return " ".join(ddl)
flowFile = session.get()
if flowFile != None: SCHEMA = json.loads(flowFile.getAttribute("SCHEMA").encode('utf-8', 'ignore')) PARTITION = flowFile.getAttribute("PARTITION") CLUSTERING = flowFile.getAttribute("CLUSTERING") CLUSTERING_NB = flowFile.getAttribute("CLUSTERING_NB") HIVE_TABLE_NAME = flowFile.getAttribute("HIVE_TABLE_NAME") HDFS_PATH = flowFile.getAttribute("HDFS_PATH") HIVE_DB = flowFile.getAttribute("HIVE_DB")
ddl = hive_ddl(HIVE_DB=HIVE_DB, SCHEMA=SCHEMA, HIVE_TABLE_NAME=HIVE_TABLE_NAME, HDFS_PATH=HDFS_PATH, PARTITION=PARTITION, CLUSTERING=CLUSTERING, CLUSTERING_NB=CLUSTERING_NB) flowFile = session.putAttribute(flowFile, "CLUSTERING_NB", CLUSTERING_NB)
flowFile = session.putAttribute(flowFile, "HIVE_DDL", ddl)
session.transfer(flowFile, REL_SUCCESS)
